description: This hall of fame Gaston purrs with a rating of 89, and a multiplier of 3x. It has a total score of 267, and confers the same amount of votes in the EtherCats DAO. The card game properties are Box for North, 1 for East, Box for South, and 1 for West. Gaston has the personality suit of whale. Each Founders Series cat is part of NFT history. These fine felines represent the first verifiably random packs minted with Chainlink VRF.
name: Gaston [267 Votes, Hall of Fame]
